      <item>
        <title>Half-Life 2 remake?</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[xalener]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>exactly. I’ve always been curious as to what HL2 style environments would look like in a mainstream current gen engine like CE3 or UE3, but it would require a complete re-everything.</p>
<p>The issue is that graphics aside, HL2 is still pretty much current gen. The acting can’t really be replaced, the models are all pretty modern standard save a few discrepancies, the only thing that could really use a major overhaul in another engine are the maps.</p>
